                            <comment id="14067694" author="hdeng" created="Sat, 19 Jul 2014 22:22:34 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The second patch &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-1972&quot; title=&quot;Fix invalid volatile long/int increment (++)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;ZOOKEEPER-1972&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;ZOOKEEPER-1972&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.patch.2&quot; is using AtomicInteger for tick as well.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t consider performance issue here for incrementing the tick.&lt;/p&gt;

